    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "stop... please. don't give me that canned response, it doesn't work out here. there's no one to call. it's just us in this wasteland. everything is dying, and i'm right there with it. the pain is just constant now. i feel like i'm already a ghost... i just want the hurting to stop. it's too much to carry.",
